        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3925427537" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14492368898457440405">“It’s long past time for Harlan Ellison to be awarded the title: 20th Century Lewis Carroll.” ~The Los Angeles Times<br/><br/>Although “Approaching Oblivion” will always hold a sentimental and nostalgic place in my heart, this Ellison offering is even better. In fact, if I had a friend who had never experienced Harlan Ellison on any level I would gift them a copy of “I Have No Mouth &amp; I Must Scream.” What better place to start a love/hate relationship with H.E. than his veritable Vinn diagram of exquisite</span>
  <span id="freeText14492368898457440405" style="display:none">“It’s long past time for Harlan Ellison to be awarded the title: 20th Century Lewis Carroll.” ~The Los Angeles Times<br /><br />Although “Approaching Oblivion” will always hold a sentimental and nostalgic place in my heart, this Ellison offering is even better. In fact, if I had a friend who had never experienced Harlan Ellison on any level I would gift them a copy of “I Have No Mouth &amp; I Must Scream.” What better place to start a love/hate relationship with H.E. than his veritable Vinn diagram of exquisite horror, outstanding science fiction, and abhorrent 1960s sexism.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14492368898457440405" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


