        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2506488487" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7435729131542711633">Such a varied collection and hard to rate. It has three of the best stories I&apos;ve ever read (I have no mouth and I must scream - Lonelyache - World of the myth). <br/><br/>The others weren&apos;t to my liking at all (Eyes of Dust was decent but the rest didn&apos;t work for me). It&apos;s also worth noting that most collections have a decent amount of stories where this only has seven, which is a bit of a rip. <br/><br/>I&apos;m ignoring the fact that Ellison was known to be a bit of a cunt. The title story is worth the price of admiss</span>
  <span id="freeText7435729131542711633" style="display:none">Such a varied collection and hard to rate. It has three of the best stories I've ever read (I have no mouth and I must scream - Lonelyache - World of the myth). <br /><br />The others weren't to my liking at all (Eyes of Dust was decent but the rest didn't work for me). It's also worth noting that most collections have a decent amount of stories where this only has seven, which is a bit of a rip. <br /><br />I'm ignoring the fact that Ellison was known to be a bit of a cunt. The title story is worth the price of admission alone and one of the most terrifying things I've ever read. </span>
